chapter:
&reftitle.setup;



 &reftitle.required;


  Compiling this extension requires mysqlnd and the following system libraries: libprotobuf, libboost, andprotobuf.
  It also requires PHP 7.1 or higher, and MySQL 5.7 or higher and MySQL 8 recommended.





 &reftitle.install;


   An example installation on Ubuntu 16.04:


   $ apt install build-essential libprotobuf-dev libboost-dev openssl protobuf-compiler 

   $ add-apt-repository ppa:ondrej/php
   $ apt install php7.1-cli php7.1-dev php7.1-mysql php7.1-pdo php7.1-xml

   $ pecl install mysql_xdevapi-alpha





 &reftitle.runtime;
 &no.config;
